at least 1,000 HP.\\n• The player must not hit any allies by direct shots.\\n• Can be obtained in Random Battles only.\", \"\", \"wot/current/achievement/mainGun.png\", \"wot/current/achievement/big/mainGun.png\", 171], [\"supporter\", false, \"battle\", \"repeatable\", \"Confederate\", \"Cause damage or critical hits to more enemy vehicles, at least 6, than any other player.\", \"• Targets that were destroyed by other players or lost in battle are included.\\n• Ricochets and non-penetrating hits are not included.\\n• Can be obtained in Random Battles only.\", \"\", \"wot/current/achievement/supporter.png\", \"wot/current/achievement/big/supporter.png\", 135], [\"medalRadleyWalters\", false, \"epic\", \"repeatable\", \"Radley-Walters\'s Medal\", \"Destroy enemy vehicles:\\n    8-9 — Standard Battle, Assault, Encounter.\\n    10-12 — Grand Battle.\", \"• In vehicles of at least Tier V.\\n• Can be obtained in Random Battles only.\", \"Sydney Valpy Radley-Walters was a Canadian tank ace of the 27th Armored Regiment. In 1944–1945 he destroyed 18 German vehicles with his Sherman Firefly.\", \"wot/current/achievement/medalRadleyWalters.png\", \"wot/current/achievement/big/medalRadleyWalters.png\", 1], [\"huntsman\", false, \"epic\", \"repeatable\", \"Naydin\'s Medal\", \"Destroy all enemy light tanks (at least 3) in the course of one battle.\", \"• Can be obtained in Random Battles only.\", \"Sergeant Grigoriy Naydin was a BT-7 commander. On June 25th, 1941, near the Lithuanian town of Rudishkyay, he destroyed a Wehrmacht armored column that included 15 vehicles and 10 guns of the 19th Mechanized Corps. Naydin managed to hold off the German advance for two days, making it possible to organize the defenses around Vilnius. For this action, Naydin was made a Hero of the Soviet Union.\", \"wot/current/achievement/huntsman.png\", \"wot/current/achievement/big/huntsman.png\", 4], [\"medalKolobanov\", false, \"epic\", \"repeatable\", \"Kolobanov\'s Medal\", \"Stand alone against at least five enemy vehicles and win.\", \"• Can be obtained in Random Battles only.\", \"Colonel Zinoviy Kolobanov was a Soviet tank ace who destroyed 22 German tanks, two guns, and two armored vehicles with his KV-1 in battle on August 19th, 1941.\", \"wot/current/achievement/medalKolobanov.png\", \"wot/current/achievement/big/medalKolobanov.png\", 1], [\"tacticalBreakthrough\", false, \"special\", \"series\", \"Tactical Genius\", \"Win at least 3 battles in a row as a member of a random team.\", \"• Every vehicle has its own series. An unbroken series continues in the next battle using the same vehicle.\\n• Can be obtained in Team Battles only.\", \"\", \"wot/current/achievement/tacticalBreakthrough.png\", \"wot/current/achievement/big/tacticalBreakthrough.png\", 4]], \"mastery\": {\"mastery_count\": 40, \"vehicles_count\": 198}, \"parameters\": [\"name\", \"deprecated\", \"section\", \"type\", \"mark\", \"description\", \"condition\", \"hero_info\", \"icon\", \"icon_big\", \"value\"], \"total_achievements_count\": 6027, \"unique_achievements_count\": 95}','{\"spa_id\": 1000562784, \"summary\": {\"is_valid\": true, \"last_battle_at\": 1610423899}, \"nickname\": \"stanly\", \"clan_info\": [], \"reg_timestamp\": 1303373642}','2026-06-05 12:55:58','ok',NULL,'2026-06-05 12:55:58','2026-06-05 12:55:58'),('na',1016813263,'Sir2000','sir2000','','','{\"wtr\": 1492, \"xp_max\": 632, \"frags_max\": 3, \"damage_max\": 472, \"wins_ratio\": 41.88, \"blocked_max\": 0, \"frags_count\": 37, \"assisted_max\": 0, \"battles_count\": 117, \"battle_avg_blocked\": 25, \"battle_avg_assisted\": 30, \"random_battles_count\": 117, \"xp_per_battle_average\": 122, \"damage_per_battle_average\": 57}','{\"tiers\": {\"1\": {\"wins_count\": 7, \"master_count\": 2, \"battles_count\": 19, \"wins_count_percent\": 36.84, \"battles_count_percent\": 16.24}, \"2\": {\"wins_count\": 21, \"master_count\": 4, \"battles_count\": 43, \"wins_count_percent\": 48.84, \"battles_count_percent\": 36.75}, \"3\":